Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who did that with the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't tell me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it didn't do anything that warned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It means... it means that from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretended to be our friend, but you truly intended to get revenge from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means that you didn't care about Lemon Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice act...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Manipulation was the only thing you were concerned about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All the effort you supposedly placed upon the members here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that have also left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All that intense training...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All the effort we put into our debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that Himuro is a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, an important person to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.56,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore. I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've come this far, you'll have to continue with me 'til the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That man destroyed the affectionate heart and life of Yui like an electric overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crush that man's arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And reveal Yui's torment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo, you'll help, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll remove that man from the music world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Miki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange to think that all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If your intention was to manipulate everyone as if they were objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you would be doing the same thing that Himuro-san did with Yui-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...You would be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go back to the old Miki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you think is best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miru-chan, you shouldn't in this condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why don't they understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kogure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did Lemon Angel turn solo?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.26,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}First Lemon Angel / 5 days left until the festival!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.81,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The first Lemon Angel announced that they will return!!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.77,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Music! News from the artistic world / Surrounded! The lost members of the second Lemon Angel participated in secret training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret training, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We won without a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,The second Lemon Angel, the dream meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you go back to being yourself for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't start to hate singing, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This festival is great, isn't it?  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is anxious to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With some music, we'll create an even better beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Yui and I wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The real...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Miki made it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.87,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear about Miki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Music is a good thing! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, about that, we would like to cancel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, true, I apologize.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.39,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Second Lemon Angel started!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's act!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Act?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been like that, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When we arrived, it was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you went to the audition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you act, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it'll be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That really annoys me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Lemon Angel, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you carrying everyone's dreams who were cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to keep looking at your face like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The doughnuts will be awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Carrying the... dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I asking to be comforted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A rare client.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't they introduce themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know. That's for them to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's repeating..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That manipulator and her awkward feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Got no patience either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.95,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her brain is too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.49,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obey, or you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.96,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound that surpasses mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably working alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you creating a suitable sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than you, at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I can present...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...because the program obeys the commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The dolls don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person that's becoming exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's testing who will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And like that, all will be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If this situation continues, victory is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect sound I wanted that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That, if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?... the solo singers returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with just you guys, it's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll train until we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How's things going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect, we can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With an easy simulation, even the body will look real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.69,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.78,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with Himuro-san's sound and my influence, we'll change...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.99,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Musical history!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We'll stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worked hard up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Compensate the lack of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...with energy and vigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The club's person spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Except Miki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sang up until now for Yui-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm becoming confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyumi got mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ann didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Said that what I learned from Ann wouldn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't change?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned Ann's music.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I could rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann really existed at that time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she doesn't exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But people that are waiting for us, do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to make the music get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The promise we made before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When we decided on the main singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked if we could surpass Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's with you... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you, I can't surpass her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Without music, it's not possible to rise above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Miru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:41.67,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, when I listen to you sing, I feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:42.55,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.14,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, will you sing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.26,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yui and I've always thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.93,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We wanted to produce real music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.14,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only by listening to music, people would find their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.40,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That incredible kind of music!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Real music?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One that could surpass everything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:07.76,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Since the first day i laid eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:07.76,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hajimete negatta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:16.11,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,For some reason my heart can't seem to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:16.11,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}nazeka kokoro ga nemuren nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:24.87,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage to pick up the phone and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:24.87,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}denwa wa suru yuuki mo nai kawari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:34.75,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Please, if for only a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:34.75,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}toomawari guuzen wo kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:39.67,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Whe girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:39.67,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}onna no ko tachi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:43.47,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:43.47,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}koi wo suru ta bi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:49.60,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,...They become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:49.60,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}sabishigari ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.39,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,As they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.39,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}itsudaatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:54.65,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:54.65,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:23:09.79,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Because when in love, this feeling says no one else but you will do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:23:09.79,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}nee kono kimochi kimi igai wa arienai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.62,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.62,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:18.59,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Hold me closer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:18.59,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Motto dakishimete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:28.30,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,and take me to a world I can only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:28.30,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yume no naka made tsuretette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:33.97,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(0,475)}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that it took me a long time to understand what Yui-senpai wanted to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you worked hard, Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but you are clumsy at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next Lemon Angel Project, episode 13, "Never Give Up"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
